<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>공지사항</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@100;300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.2.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-xh6O/CkQoPOWDdYTDqeRdPCVd1SpvCA9XXcUnZS2FmJNp1coAFzvtCN9BmamE+4aHK8yyUHUSCcJHgXloTyT2A==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/css.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div id="header__mobileAd">
            <span>
                <strong>해야짐</strong>이 처음이신가요? 지금 바로 체험해보세요!
            </span>
            <a href="">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen"></i>
                <span>앱 다운로드</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div id="header__main">
            <a href="/"><img src="/logo/logo.png" id="header__logo"></a>
            <nav>
                        <%= nick %>
                        <a href="/MyPage">마이페이지</a> 
                        <a href="/Calendar">운동달력</a> 
                        <a href="/Board/list">커뮤니티</a> 
                        <a href="/auth/logout">로그아웃</a>   
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="board_wrap">
        <div class="board_title">
            <strong>커뮤니티</strong>
            <p</p>
        </div>
        <form name="save" action="/board/save" method="post">
        <div class="board_write_wrap">
            <div class="board_write">
                <div class="title">
                    <dl>
                        <dt>제목</dt>
                        <dd><input type="text" name="brdtitle"  value="<%=row.brdtitle%>"></dd>
                    </dl>
                </div>
                <div class="info">
                    <dl>
                    <div class="info_wrap">
                    <dt>상태</dt>
                    
                    <dd><div class="info_status"><input type="radio" name="category" value="정보" class="status" required>정보</div>
                    <dd><div class="info_match"><input type="radio" name="category" value="구인" class="match">구인</div>
                    </div>
                    </dl>
                </div>
                <div class="cont">
                    <textarea name="brdmemo"><%=row.brdmemo%></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bt_wrap">
                <input type="submit" value="등록" class="on">
                <a href="/board/list">취소</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <input type="hidden" name="brdno" value="<%=row.brdno%>"> </form>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div>
            <nav id="footer__nav">
                <a href="">ⓒHaeyagym.co.kr</a>
                <a href="">이용약관</a>
                <a href="">운영정책</a>
                <a href="">개인정보처리방침</a>
                <a href="">환불규정</a>
            </nav>
            <div id="footer__info">
                <strong>(주)해야짐</strong><br> 
                <span>대표 이혁주 | 8221 서울시 구로구 경인로 445 ([구]고척동 62-160) 동양미래대학교</span><br>
                <span>(주)해야짐은 통신판매중개자이며 통신판매의 당사자가 아닙니다. 따라서 (주)해야짐은 상품, 거래정보 및 거래에 대하여 책임을 지지 않습니다.</span>
            </div>  
            <div id="footer__contact">
                <p>고객센터</p>
                <div id="footer__contact__kakao">
                    <img src="img/kakaotalk_sharing_btn_medium.png" >
                    <span>카카오톡 상담</span>
                </div>
                <span>평일 09:00 ~ 18:00(점심시간 13:00 ~ 14:00)</span>
                <span>주말 및 공휴일은 쉽니다..</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>